#. <section class="sutta" id="sn7.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn7.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Arahantavagga"
msgstr "1. The Perfected Ones"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn7.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Ahiṃsakasutta"
msgstr "5. Harmless"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.165"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.5:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn7.5:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho ahiṃsakabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then the brahmin Bhāradvāja the Harmless went up to the Buddha, and "
"exchanged greetings with him."

msgctxt "sn7.5:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho ahiṃsakabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side and said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn7.5:1.4"
msgid "“ahiṃsakāhaṃ, bho gotama, ahiṃsakāhaṃ, bho gotamā”ti."
msgstr "“I am Harmless, Master Gotama, I am Harmless!”"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.353"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.5:2.1"
msgid "“Yathā nāmaṃ tathā cassa,"
msgstr "“If you were really like your name,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.5:2.2"
msgid "siyā kho tvaṃ ahiṃsako;"
msgstr "then you’d be Harmless."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.5:2.3"
msgid "Yo ca kāyena vācāya,"
msgstr "But a truly harmless person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.5:2.4"
msgid "manasā ca na hiṃsati;"
msgstr "does no harm by way of"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.5:2.5"
msgid "Sa ve ahiṃsako hoti,"
msgstr "body, speech, or mind;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.5:2.6"
msgid "yo paraṃ na vihiṃsatī”ti."
msgstr "they don’t harm anyone else.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.5:3.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, ahiṃsakabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When he had spoken, the brahmin Bhāradvāja the Harmless said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn7.5:3.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! …” …"

msgctxt "sn7.5:3.3"
msgid "abbhaññāsi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn7.5:3.4"
msgid "Aññataro ca panāyasmā ahiṃsakabhāradvājo arahataṃ ahosīti."
msgstr "And Venerable Bhāradvāja the Harmless became one of the perfected."
